testimonials.text: Francisco is a hardworking, determined developer who doesn't back down from a challenge. He has proven time and time again that he is willing to make the moves required to meet standards and deadlines. His work ethic is astounding and he always brings positive energy to those around him. He puts in the time and it shows in his work. Francisco's ability to work on his duties while being available to help others makes him a great team player and developer

I've had the opportunity to collaborate with Francisco on a few coding projects and he has steadily proven his determination at problem solving. Not only did his proficiency in both front and backend development help drive our projects into successful completion, he is also a great team player - always willing to help others overcome roadblocks and continuously supported troubleshooting efforts without hesitation!
